description:
This is a double exposure, the first shot is my friend, and as I was taking the photo, I just noticed that there was a digital clock on the ground nearby, and it was 9:43, so I told my friend that when 10:10:10 comes around, I want to capture the clock, and put it on your portrait, so I had to be very careful to catch the picture at 10:10:10. I was successful!

Gear I used
Camera: Nikon FM10 
Lens: 35~70 1:3.5~4.8 
Film: Fujicolor C200

Technique: Double Exposure
